@using lltg._1688.rponey.cc.Model
@using RPoney.Utilty.Extend
@model lltg._1688.rponey.cc.Model.Entity.ShareArticleEntity
<div class="wrapper wrapper-content animated fadeInRight">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="ibox float-e-margins">
                <div class="ibox-content">
                    <form class="form-horizontal m-t" method="POST" action="@Url.Action("Save")" onsubmit="return DoAjaxPostSubmitForm(this)">
                        @Html.HiddenFor(m => m.Id)
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="col-sm-3 control-label">标题：</label>
                            <div class="col-sm-8">
                                @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.Title)
                                <span class="help-block m-b-none"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> 标题不能为空</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="col-sm-3 control-label">类型：</label>
                            <div class="col-sm-8">
                                <select name="ArticleType">
                                    @foreach (var articleType in EnumExtend.GetEnumRemarks<PublicEnum.ShareArticleTypeEnum>())
                                    {
                                        if ((int) Model.ArticleType == articleType.Key)
                                        {
                                            <option value="@articleType.Key" selected="selected">@articleType.Value</option>
                                        }
                                        else
                                        {
                                            <option value="@articleType.Key">@articleType.Value</option>
                                        }
                                    }
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="col-sm-3 control-label"> 文章链接：</label>
                            <div class="col-sm-8">
                                @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.ArticleUrl)
                                <span class="help-block m-b-none"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> 文章链接地址不能为空</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="col-sm-3 control-label">封面地址：</label>
                            <div class="col-sm-8">
                                @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.Cover)
                                <span class="help-block m-b-none"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> 请选择封面图片</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-3">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">提交</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
